    "faq_tag": "Frequently Asked Questions",
    "faq_1_q": "What exactly do I receive every week?",
    "faq_1_a": "For each UFC card: complete pre-fight analysis (15 sections for main card, 6 for prelims), Creator Kit with ready-to-post content for Instagram, Twitter/X, YouTube, TikTok and Podcast, and after the event, a recap with prediction audit.",
